Class ValidationException

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Exception

jsweet.lang.Error
framework.components.api.ValidationException
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ValidationException
extends jsweet.lang.Error
Exception used for validation purposes.
This exception is thrown by InputField when performing validation.
It has facilities to hold and tranfer error messages and codes in a generic way
There is no UI rendering performed by this class. The UI rendering is delegated to the component throwing this exception
The component will know better how to display the message
Author:
Rossaye Abdool Kureem Apr 15, 2018
